in the UK,

328
00:16:18,359 --> 00:16:19,159
I joined

329
00:16:19,239 --> 00:16:20,840
BlackRock in the UK.

330
00:16:21,119 --> 00:16:22,320
In those years,

331
00:16:22,559 --> 00:16:24,840
