334
00:16:31,760 --> 00:16:32,880
What's the reason?

335
00:16:33,919 --> 00:16:35,799
Do you know
the Minsheng Road in Shanghai?

336
00:16:36,159 --> 00:16:37,039
I

337
00:16:37,559 --> 00:16:39,200
was the chief trader

338
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:40,479
