355
00:17:41,199 --> 00:17:41,760
Let's go.

356
00:18:12,800 --> 00:18:13,599
Mr. Lei.

357
00:18:14,719 --> 00:18:15,520
Mr. Lei.

358
00:18:15,640 --> 00:18:16,520
Guys.

359
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:19,680
Hello, uncle Duan.

360
00:18:19,680 --> 00:18:20,920
